'''薩茨維'''（{{lang-ka|საცივი}}）是一道[[喬治亞|喬治亞]]傳統菜餚，主要由[[核桃|核桃]]製成。薩茨維有多種烹飪方式<ref name="SatsiviGeorgianRecipies">[http://georgianrecipes.net/2014/01/02/satsivi/ Satsivi] {{Wayback|url=http://georgianrecipes.net/2014/01/02/satsivi/ |date=20210507023041 }}. Georgian Recipes by [http://georgiaabout.com/ Georgia About] {{Wayback|url=http://georgiaabout.com/ |date=20210503010811 }}. 2014</ref>。薩茨維除了可以作為甜食食用之外<ref name="BazheGeorgianRecipies">[http://georgianrecipes.net/2013/03/29/bazhe-sauce/ Bazhe sauce] {{Wayback|url=http://georgianrecipes.net/2013/03/29/bazhe-sauce/ |date=20210123050403 }}. Georgian Recipes by [http://georgiaabout.com/ Georgia About] {{Wayback|url=http://georgiaabout.com/ |date=20210503010811 }}. 2013</ref>，也可以是肉類料理的一部分<ref>[http://georgianrecipes.net/2013/12/26/eggplant-satsivi/ Eggplant satsivi] {{Wayback|url=http://georgianrecipes.net/2013/12/26/eggplant-satsivi/ |date=20210504000804 }}. Georgian Recipes by [http://georgiaabout.com/ Georgia About] {{Wayback|url=http://georgiaabout.com/ |date=20210503010811 }}. 2013</ref><ref>[http://georgianrecipes.net/2013/11/18/cauliflower-satsivi/ Cauliflower satsivi] {{Wayback|url=http://georgianrecipes.net/2013/11/18/cauliflower-satsivi/ |date=20210124122618 }}. Georgian Recipes by [http://georgiaabout.com/ Georgia About] {{Wayback|url=http://georgiaabout.com/ |date=20210503010811 }}. 2013</ref>。
